      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "And they were responsible for the rescue of Lady Victoria from the [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganRestoration],Restoration]] after she was captured by the Ghost Riders.\n\nPlus, they also participated in the assault at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSmithon],Smithon]] were Lord Karosas was killed.",
