    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ccf1ab5750845f5be9d2d7d"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "These guys are definitely trouble just from what I've seen so far from their 'Mechs. They're loaded with [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLosTech],lostech]] improvements to their jump jets or [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMyomer],myomers]]. ",
      "branches": [
        {
