    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cbcc649072bae16ab3e07b2"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "And their small size makes them very difficult to detect... the [[DM.Factions[faction_Liao],Capellans]] already paid dearly for mistreating them, since they made a series of high-value raids after the Angels turned on House Liao.\n\nBut they do have one vulnerability, the need of a base to sustain themselves while striking the Restoration's backdoor.",
      "branches": [
        {
