    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c13a38a4956fff084593f58"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "There's a major split amongst the Creed concerning the civil war and the Taurian intervention, which was why she left.\n\nAs long as we keep Lady Kamea and Alexander out of sight, we should be fine since the Angels' presence isn't much appreciated on this world.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Very well, XO. What else do you have on the Angels' headquarters?",
