        "id": "9c993f270c660e3d0d826988"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Alright, alright, I don't want to be the dissenting voice around here.\n\nKamea and Alexander are poking around the <i>Argo</i>, I'd better check on them and make sure they don't get into trouble.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Very well, let's take down the Angels.",
